data.description: Are you looking for a home with a Mother-in-Law set up or 2nd Living area for Roommates or other Household members? This Full Remodel- has 2 Full Kitchens, 2 Living Rooms, 4-bed, 2-bath, 2-car garage plus RV parking. Impeccably Renovated in 2023. Renovation Includes: • Brand-New Appliances in Both Kitchens • New Samsung Flex Washer/Dryer package • New Counters & Cabinets • Fresh Texture & Paint throughout • All New Baseboards, Doors, Trim, Vent Registers, & Outlets/Switches Covers • New -Flooring, Windows, & Sliding Glass Door • New Tile, Tub, & Vanities • ALL NEW Fixtures & Hardware- incl lights, fans, faucets, sinks, doorknobs and more… • New Water Heater & Garbage Disposal Outside: • Fresh Paint • New Stairs & Deck/Landing • New Garage Doors & Downspouts • New Sprinkler Heads and Valves • New Lights & Vents Landscaped w/ Sprinkler System on a Spacious Lot, all without HOA restrictions.
